cn.jpush.im.api

Class BasicCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.jpush.im.api.BasicCallback
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommandNotificationEvent.GetTargetInfoCallback, CreateGroupCallback, DownloadAvatarCallback, DownloadCompletionCallback, GetAvatarBitmapCallback, GetBlacklistCallback, GetGroupIDListCallback, GetGroupInfoCallback, GetGroupInfoListCallback, GetGroupMembersCallback, GetNoDisurbListCallback, GetReceiptDetailsCallback, GetUserInfoCallback, GetUserInfoListCallback, ImageContent.CreateImageContentCallback, IntegerCallback, ProgressUpdateCallback

    public abstract class BasicCallback
extends java.lang.Object
    默认 JPush IM 的所有 callback 都是主线程调用回去。一般也不会有问题。

    但如果callback 回去后 App 侧有比较重的任务，可选让 JPush IM SDK Callback 回去时在子线程。
